dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Telegraph Peak and Phelan quadrangles, San Bernardino County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Geology Telegraph Peak and Phelan quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base maps from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangles TELEGRAPH PEAK AND PHELAN, CA 1988, DMA 2452 I SE - Series V895"
"Prepared in cooperation with the Angeles National Forest."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, index to sources of geology, and 2 col. cross sections.
